nz.org.p2p.model.event.api
Interface EventService

All Known Subinterfaces:
IEvent
public interface EventService

The event service interface encapsulates public event information suitable for event promotion and management. This software is offered under the terms of the GNU AFERO GENERAL PUBLIC LICENCE of 2007, See package documentation for more information.

Author:
John Hutcheson <witerat@gmail.com>, Richard Thomas <richard@kanecta.com>
